=head1 DESCRIPTION

Details about an Amazon RDS event notification subscription. The
subscription allows Amazon RDS to post events to an SNS topic.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 CustomerAwsId => Str

The identifier of the event notification subscription.


=head2 CustSubscriptionId => Str

The identifier of the account that is associated with the event
notification subscription.


=head2 Enabled => Bool

Whether the event notification subscription is enabled.


=head2 EventCategoriesList => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

The list of event categories for the event notification subscription.


=head2 EventSubscriptionArn => Str

The ARN of the event notification subscription.


=head2 SnsTopicArn => Str

The ARN of the SNS topic to post the event notifications to.


=head2 SourceIdsList => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

A list of source identifiers for the event notification subscription.


=head2 SourceType => Str

The source type for the event notification subscription.


=head2 Status => Str

The status of the event notification subscription.

Valid values: C<creating> | C<modifying> | C<deleting> | C<active> |
C<no-permission> | C<topic-not-exist>


=head2 SubscriptionCreationTime => Str

The datetime when the event notification subscription was created.

